{
  "name": "Branch Family Training",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Hyuga.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p>\n<p>Prerequisite: Hyūga Clan</p>\n<p>You train with members of the other branch of your clan, you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>• Increase your Dexterity or Wisdom score by 1, to a Maximum of 20. </p>\n<p><br />• You can learn jutsu from the opposite branch. <br />If you are a main branch, you can learn side branch Hyūga Jutsu. <br />If you are a side branch you can learn main branch Hyūga Jutsu. </p>\n<p><br />• You learn one additional Hyūga clan Hijutsu that you qualify for. </p>\n<p><br />• You can create and learn Hyūga clan Hijutsu in half the required time and with half the required cost.</p>",
